            <title>Assassin&#8217;s Creed 游戏中弹全屏广告　Ubisoft: 技术问题非原意</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/25/ubisoft-assassins-creed-odyssey-pop-up-ad/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ubisoft-assassins-creed-odyssey-pop-up-ad</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/25/ubisoft-assassins-creed-odyssey-pop-up-ad/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 25 Nov 2023 13:10:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[assassin's creed]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[刺客教条]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1206884</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>游戏中出现广告并非新鲜事，不过在家用游戏机上的大作于游戏途中弹出全画面广告则相当罕见。最近 Assassin&#8217;s Creed Odyssey 玩家发现开启地图画面时竟然出现巨型广告，Ubisoft 则解释这并非设计原意。<br /><span id="more-1206884"></span></p><p>最近在 Reddit 上，有 Assassin&#8217;s Creed Odyssey 的玩家表示，在游戏进行中每次开启地图画面，都会出现 Ubisoft Black Friday 优惠的全画面广告，对于游戏体验有很大影响。这个问题似乎在 Xbox 和 PlayStation 版本中都有出现。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">We have been made aware that some players encountered a pop-up message in-game while playing certain Assassin’s Creed titles yesterday. This was the result of a technical error that has now been fixed.</p><p>Our intention was to display a promotion for Assassin&#39;s Creed Mirage as part…</p><p>&mdash; Assassin&#39;s Creed (@assassinscreed) <a href="https://twitter.com/assassinscreed/status/1728105025979679011?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 24, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>Ubisoft 后来回应消息表示，他们确认了在部分 Assassin&#8217;s Creed 游戏中，玩家会遇到弹出式广告的问题，解释这是技术问题，已经在发现之后尽快解决。原先这个弹出式广告是打算在 Assassin&#8217;s Creed Mirage 以外的系列作品的主选单画面加入，不过由于技术问题，这个广告就出现在游戏内的选单画面中。不过无论如何，玩家真心白银买了游戏之后竟然又有广告出现，确实是个相当扰人的问题。</p><p>了爱用：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/24/23974420/ubisoft-assassins-creed-odyssey-pop-up-ad-xbox-playstation-technical-error">Verge</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

